                <td rowspan="1" colspan="1">Provide refresher training to primary care physicians (100% coverage in 5 years)</td>
                <td rowspan="1" colspan="1">Improve referral patterns</td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <td rowspan="1" colspan="1"/>
                <td align="left" rowspan="1" colspan="1">Provide refresher training to primary care physicians (at least 50% coverage in 5 years).</td>
                <td rowspan="1" colspan="1"/>
                <td rowspan="1" colspan="1"/>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <td align="left" rowspan="1" colspan="1">2. Make appropriate treatments available</td>
                <td align="left" rowspan="1" colspan="1">Increase availability of essential drugs for the treatment of dementia and associated psychological and behavioural symptoms.</td>
                <td align="left" rowspan="1" colspan="1">Ensure availability of essential drugs in all healthcare settings.</td>
