<list list-type="simple"><list-item><p>&#x2013; Legal framework to support and protect those with impaired mental capacity</p></list-item><list-item><p>&#x2013; Inclusion of people with dementia in disability benefit schemes</p></list-item><list-item><p>&#x2013; Inclusion of caregivers in compensatory benefit schemes</p></list-item></list></td>
